column18:
Welcome to the study on subjective judgement of body poses. 
 

This questionnaire consists of multiple blocks, where one random picture of a 3D human model performing an action will be shown. It will be followed by a set of 10 questions, and in total, the whole experiment is expected to take 1h30minutes to complete. More details regarding the procedure will be further explained in the next sections.

 

Upon its completion you will receive a  reward that can be redeemed via 3 options(1.5 SONA credits, VVV voucher and Reimbursement equivalent to 15 euros ). At the end of the experiment, you will be guided on how to do it.



Your participation in the study is voluntary and you can withdraw your participation at anytime. The data collected here will only be used for research purposes and will not be publicly disclosed. 

In case you still have any questions, please feel free to contact: g.marrazzo@maastrichtuniversity.nl



Do you consent to this terms?
